==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skylarking
<hw>Sky"lark"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of running about the
rigging of a vessel in sport; hence, frolicking; scuffing; sporting;
carousing.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

